description:
A collection of utilities bringing back classic features to Windows.


What's Changed
- Add ARM64 support by @Mattiwatti in https://github.com/Open-Shell/Open-Shell-Menu/pull/641
- ExplorerPatcher compatibility by @ge0rdi in https://github.com/Open-Shell/Open-Shell-Menu/pull/2107
Full Changelog: https://github.com/Open-Shell/Open-Shell-Menu/compare/v4.4.195...v4.4.196
[!IMPORTANT]
Note for ARM64 users
Recent Windows 11 on ARM64 may block setup due to previous incompatibility with the platform.
If you encounter a message saying This application can't run on this device, just rename setup to something like OpenShell.exe and run again.
